0D2B7D9E.Line39.BAE4: Lilith’s petals. Her blood was fed to me, once.

188E5817.Line37.B6582: I...I don’t know. Will you let me try? I want to try.

7EB30ECB.Line35.BD31C: You've read so much, yet know so little. Will you accept my offer?

912480F8.Line5.BD31C: How your mind races. Yes, I am Lilith. Mother of Sanctuary.

927139EA.Line25.BD31C: Is that what you want to believe? Drop the act. You have questions, I have answers. I know the fabric of the cosmos.
